    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s in such incredible, pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect and ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions; I\u2019d love to see this beauty go to a great home!",
      "price": 44500.0,
