      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive masterpiece: a time-capsule specimen preserved in showroom-fresh state. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a professional ceramic coating that makes the original paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains untouched by time, featuring supple, uncreased leather that still carries that signature new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and electronic component functions with factory-spec precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, having been exclusively garage-kept and maintained with an open checkbook. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment for the most discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. From the pristine undercarriage to the flawless alloy wheels, this vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 46500.0,
